l_server.py\n\n@app.get(\"/attribution/{file_path}\")\ndef get_attribution(file_path: str, line: int):\n    \"\"\"Free, local attribution lookup\"\"\"\n    storage = SQLiteStorage()\n    return storage.get_attribution(file_path, line)\n\n@app.get(\"/search\")  # Not available in local mode\ndef search(query: str):\n    return {\"error\": \"Search requires cloud mode\"}\n```\n\n**Cloud API (Commercial):**\n```python\n# devmemory-cloud/api/server.py\n\n@app.get(\"/search\")\n@require_subscription(\"pro\")\ndef search(query: str, user: User):\n    \"\"\"Advanced semantic search (commercial)\"\"\"\n    return intelligence_engine.search(query, user.namespace)\n\n@app.get(\"/analytics\")\n@require_subscription(\"pro\")\ndef get_analytics(user: User):\n    \"\"\"Team analytics (commercial)\"\"\"\n    return analytics_engine.get_team_metrics(user.team_id)\n\n@app.post(\"/governance/policy\")\n@require_subscription(\"enterprise\")\ndef create_policy(policy: Policy, user: User):\n    \"\"\"Policy management (enterprise only)\"\"\"\n    return governance_engine.create_policy(policy, user.org_id)\n```\n\n### 4. Deployment Options\n\n**Option A: SaaS (Cloud)**\n```\nDeveloper → devmemory.ai → Cloud API → Redis/PostgreSQL\n                                ↓\n                          Commercial Features\n```\n\n**Option B: Self-Hosted (Enterprise)**\n```\nEnterprise → Their Infrastructure → Docker Compose\n                                        ↓\n                              Open Source + Enterprise Binary\n```\n\n**Implementation:**\n```yaml\n# docker-compose.yml (Enterprise)\nversion: '3.8'\nservices:\n  devmemory-api:\n    image: devmemory/enterprise:latest\n    environment:\n      - LICENSE_KEY=${LICENSE_KEY}\n      - DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...\n    volumes:\n      - ./config:/app/config\n```\n\nThe enterprise Docker image includes both open source and closed source components, validated by license key.\n\n---\n\n## Community Strategy\n\n### 1. Build Trust with Open Core