d Redis instructions\n```\n\n### Why\n```\n- Simplifies package (no Redis deps)\n- Smaller install size\n- Clear value proposition\n- Protects commercial features\n- Easier maintenance\n```\n\n---\n\n## Three-Phase Evolution\n\n### Phase 1: Attribution (Q1-Q2 2026)\n**Theme:** \"Clean separation, single package\"\n\n**Month 1-2:**\n```\n✅ Remove Redis/AMS from open source\n✅ Simplify to SQLite-only local mode\n✅ Create HTTP API client for cloud\n✅ Clean up dependencies\n✅ Fix installation issues\n```\n\n**Month 3-6:**\n```\n✅ Launch cloud API (private beta)\n✅ Basic cloud features (search, stats)\n✅ Dashboard MVP\n✅ API documentation\n```\n\n**Success:**\n- 1,000 local mode users\n- 100 cloud mode users\n- $5K MRR\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: Intelligence (Q3-Q4 2026)\n**Theme:** \"API-powered intelligence\"\n\n**Open Source:**\n```\n✅ Stable local mode\n✅ Bug fixes only\n✅ Community contributions\n```\n\n**Cloud API (Commercial):**\n```\n💰 Decision rationale extraction\n💰 Pattern detection\n💰 \"Why this code?\" queries\n💰 Recommendations\n💰 Team knowledge base\n```\n\n**Package:**\n```\n📡 API client updates\n📡 New cloud commands\n📡 Caching for offline use\n```\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: Governance (2027)\n**Theme:** \"Enterprise platform\"\n\n**Cloud API:**\n```\n💰 Policy engine\n💰 Compliance reports\n💰 Audit logs\n💰 SSO integration\n💰 On-premise option (Docker)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Pricing\n\n### Free (Local Mode)\n```\n$0 forever\n- SQLite storage\n- Core attribution\n- Git integration\n- Works offline\n- Community support\n```\n\n### Pro ($29/dev/month)\n```\nCloud API access\n- Semantic search\n- Team analytics\n- Basic intelligence\n- 10K API calls/month\n- Email support\n```\n\n### Enterprise (Custom)\n```\n- Higher API quotas\n- SSO integration\n- On-premise option\n- Dedicated support\n- SLA\n```\n\n---\n\n## Technical Benefits\n\n### For Users\n```\n✅ Smaller package (no Redis deps)\n✅ Simpler installation\n✅ Clear local vs cloud distinction\n✅ No infrastructure to man