ain_why()\n    ↓\nHTTP POST to: https://aiprove.org/api/v1/why\n    ↓\nNext.js API receives request\n    ↓\nReturns: {explanation, history, commits, ...}\n    ↓\nCLI displays results\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 Testing\n\n### Without API Key\n```bash\ndevmemory why src/test.py\n# Shows: \"⚠ This feature requires Cloud Edition\"\n```\n\n### With API Key\n```bash\ndevmemory config set api_key dev_test_key\ndevmemory why src/test.py\n# Calls API and shows results\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Next Steps\n\n1. **Deploy Next.js API** to aiprove.org\n2. **Implement Redis/AMS** in API endpoints (Phase 2B)\n3. **Add real data** to search, stats, why endpoints\n4. **Add dashboard** for web UI\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Files Changed\n\n**Next.js (aiprove.org):**\n- `src/app/api/v1/search/route.ts`\n- `src/app/api/v1/stats/route.ts`\n- `src/app/api/v1/why/route.ts` (NEW)\n- `src/app/api/v1/add/route.ts` (NEW)\n- `src/app/api/v1/learn/route.ts` (NEW)\n- `src/app/api/v1/context/route.ts` (NEW)\n- `src/app/api/v1/attribution/query/route.ts`\n\n**Python (devmemory):**\n- `devmemory/attribution/cloud_storage.py` - Added API methods\n- `devmemory/commands/search.py` - Uses Cloud API\n- `devmemory/commands/stats.py` - Uses Cloud API\n- `devmemory/commands/why.py` - Uses Cloud API\n- `devmemory/commands/add.py` - Uses Cloud API\n- `devmemory/cli.py` - Activated all commands\n\n---\n\n**Status:** Phase 2A Complete - All API endpoints ready, CLI commands calling APIs 🎉\n",
